    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zoe, a young, adventurous Elementalist woke up in a strange library. Travel across peculiar worlds and help her find the way back home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Elementalist is a challenging movement puzzle platformer, where you collect elemental orbs that give you powers, such as double jump, horizontal dash, ground slam, and teleporting shot. After you collect a power, it will be the next one you use, so be careful about the order of your actions. Some puzzles will require you to think outside the box.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect movement abilities in an Elemental Stack.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029010/extras/c889118d685698399df7d109fd3b2fa8.poster.avif?t=1767465021\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029010/extras/c889118d685698399df7d109fd3b2fa8.webm?t=1767465021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029010/extras/c889118d685698399df7d109fd3b2fa8.mp4?t=1767465021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use the most recently collected ability with just one button.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029010/extras/553621dad0e7ecd9c53bd858dfc2eef1.poster.avif?t=1767465021\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029010/extras/553621dad0e7ecd9c53bd858dfc2eef1.webm?t=1767465021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029010/extras/553621dad0e7ecd9c53bd858dfc2eef1.mp4?t=1767465021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>And much, much more!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029010/extras/d61cb4507ce90bf08e02fdf5b24bf948.avif?t=1767465021\" width=800 height=292 /></span></p>",
